  <Docs>
    <summary>Represents the security settings for the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding" />.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[

## Remarks
 The <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpBinding> class is designed for interoperation with services that implement WS-* specifications. The transport security for this binding is Secure Sockets Layer (SSL) over HTTP, or HTTPS.

 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
